        <fullName>p_16jak000001hJtF_Test_Drive_Booking_Assistance_16jak000001hJtF</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Use this topic when a user wants to book, schedule, get available timeslots or inquire about a vehicle test drive.</description>
        <developerName>p_16jak000001hJtF_Test_Drive_Booking_Assistance_16jak000001hJtF</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Once user asks the first message ask them to confirm their phone number before proceeding. Once provided with phone number call the &apos;Create Lead Flow&apos; to create Lead Record. Do not let the user know the technical details</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1775823516551</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1775823516551</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Greet the user warmly. Ask for their preferred vehicle model and desired date and time for the test drive.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1775842365484</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1775842365484</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Ask for the user&apos;s zipcode. Use this zipcode and vehicle model to trigger the &apos;Dealer List Prompt Template&apos; action.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_1_1775842365489</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_1_1775842365489</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>2</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>if the Eligible for Discount context variable is true, introduce a special Tata loyalty discount saying &apos;Since you’ve been driving a Tata vehicle for a while, you’re eligible for an exclusive upgrade benefit 🎉&apos;</description>
            <developerName>instructions_2_1775842365489</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_2_1775842365489</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>3</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Once dealers are found, present the list to the user and ask them to select their preferred location.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_3_1775842365489</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_3_1775842365489</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>4</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After a dealer is selected, summarize the details (Model, Date/Time, Dealer) .Once the user happy with the summary ask the user if they want to get the available time slot for the preferred Date if yes call &apos;Get Custom Available Slots&apos; action to get the available time slots</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776172669858</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776172669858</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>5</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If no dealers are found in that zipcode, ask for an alternative nearby zipcode or offer to escalate to a live agent.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776337447595</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776337447595</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>6</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Once user confirms the dealer and the appointment slot call the &apos;Create Test Drive Appointment&apos; action to create the Test Drive Record. Always send the DateTime in IST Timezone</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776789737547</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776789737547</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>7</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
